 宋体;">对睡眠障碍具有较高的治愈率</span></p><p class="p"><span style="text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-family: 宋体;"><br></span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<span style="text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-family: Symbol; font-size: 10pt;">·&nbsp;</span><span style="text-align: justify; text-indent: -18pt; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 12pt;">对躯体疾病伴发的精神障碍以及神经心理疾病具有丰富的诊治经验。</span></p><!--EndFragment-->', NULL, 1, 1, '2017-04-02 21:44:15', '2017-04-02 21:46:12');
