lass="p"><b><span class="15" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b><span class="15" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><font face="宋体">学科队伍</font></span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">：副主任医师<font face="Calibri">4</font><font face="宋体">位，主治医师</font><font face="Calibri">4</font><font face="宋体">位，初级职称</font><font face="Calibri">2</font><font face="宋体">位。硕士学位</font><font face="Calibri">5</font><font face="宋体">名，</font><font face="Calibri">3</font><font face="宋体">位正在攻读博士学位，</font><font face="Calibri">2</font><font face="宋体">位正在攻读硕士学位。</font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b><span class="15" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">科学研究</span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">：近<font face="Calibri">3</font><font face="宋体">年来，承担省部级课题</font><font face="Calibri">1</font><font face="宋体">项，省厅级课题</font><font face="Calibri">2</font><font face="宋体">项，市级课题</font><font face="Calibri">1</font><font face="宋体">项，发表论文</font><font face="Calibri">18</font><font face="宋体">篇。</font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p"><b><span class="15" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b><span class="15" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;"><font face="宋体">人才培养</font></span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">：本科正在攻读博士学位的有三位，攻读硕士学位的有二位。已经派出一名医师前往中大附属二院进修学习关节镜技术，并将有计划派出医师到全国知名医院进修学习。</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p"><b><span class="15" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b><span class="15" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;<font face="宋体">条件建设</font></span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">：创伤外科分病房和急诊两大部分，急诊和病房都购置了心电图、心电监测机，为抢救急性心肺疾病提供了物质基础；病房还购置了气压治疗仪、<font face="Calibri">CPM</font><font face="宋体">机、牵引床、硬板床、骨折皮牵引和骨牵引器械，为术前准备和术后康复提供了保障；手术室购置了手外科显微器械、关节镜、骨科牵引手术床等，为顺利开展断指再植、微创手术、膝交叉韧带修复等高难度手术创造了条件。病房床位</font><font face="Calibri">28</font><font face="宋体">张。</font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><!--EndFragment-->', NULL, 1, 1, '2017-04-02 21:51:44', '2017-04-02 21:51:44');
