l Shading Accent 6" ></w:LsdException>\n<w:LsdException Locked="false"  Priority="99"  SemiHidden="false"  Name="Colorful List Accent 6" ></w:LsdException>\n<w:LsdException Locked="false"  Priority="99"  SemiHidden="false"  Name="Colorful Grid Accent 6" ></w:LsdException>\n</w:LatentStyles></xml><![endif]--><style>\n@font-face{\nfont-family:"Times New Roman";\n}\n\n@font-face{\nfont-family:"宋体";\n}\n\n@font-face{\nfont-family:"Calibri";\n}\n\np.MsoNormal{\nmso-style-name:正文;\nmso-style-parent:"";\nmargin:0pt;\nmargin-bottom:.0001pt;\nmso-pagination:none;\ntext-align:justify;\ntext-justify:inter-ideograph;\nfont-family:Calibri;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\nfont-size:10.5000pt;\nmso-font-kerning:1.0000pt;\n}\n\nspan.10{\nfont-family:\'Times New Roman\';\n}\n\nspan.15{\nfont-family:\'Times New Roman\';\nfont-weight:bold;\n}\n\np.p{\nmso-style-name:"普通\\(网站\\)";\nmargin-top:5.0000pt;\nmargin-right:0.0000pt;\nmargin-bottom:5.0000pt;\nmargin-left:0.0000pt;\nmso-margin-top-alt:auto;\nmso-margin-bottom-alt:auto;\nmso-pagination:none;\ntext-align:left;\nfont-family:Calibri;\nmso-fareast-font-family:宋体;\nmso-bidi-font-family:\'Times New Roman\';\nfont-size:12.0000pt;\n}\n\nspan.msoIns{\nmso-style-type:export-only;\nmso-style-name:"";\ntext-decoration:underline;\ntext-underline:single;\ncolor:blue;\n}\n\nspan.msoDel{\nmso-style-type:export-only;\nmso-style-name:"";\ntext-decoration:line-through;\ncolor:red;\n}\n@page{mso-page-border-surround-header:no;\n	mso-page-border-surround-footer:no;}@page Section0{\n}\ndiv.Section0{page:Section0;}</style><!--StartFragment--><p class="p"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">普外一区（肝胆外科）成立于<font face="Calibri">1993</font><font face="宋体">年，</font><font face="Calibri">1994</font><font face="宋体">年完成我院首例腹腔镜手术（胆囊切除术）；同年开展规则性肝切除、大肝癌切除包括肝三叶切除、肝门部胆管癌根治性手术。</font><font face="Calibri">2000</font><font face="宋体">年完成了市属医疗系统首例肝脏移植手术。经过近</font><font face="Calibri">20</font><font face="宋体">年的发展，在危重疾病救治和腹部外科尤其是肝胆胰专科方向逐步形成了较强的专科特色。</font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><b><span class="15" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;1.<font face="宋体">原发性肝癌</font></span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">：对于无法<font face="Calibri">1</font><font face="宋体">期手术切除的中晚期原发性肝癌，进行介入栓塞化疗后</font><font face="Calibri">2</font><font face="宋体">期切除，取得良好疗效，术后</font><font face="Calibri">1</font><font face="宋体">，</font><font face="Calibri">2</font><font face="宋体">年内生存率分别达</font><font face="Calibri">62.5%</font><font face="宋体">和</font><font face="Calibri">37.5%</font><font face="宋体">，部分患者最长生存期超过</font><font face="Calibri">10</font><font face="宋体">年，迄今各种类型的肝癌切除手术已达</font><font face="Calibri">1000</font><font face="宋体">余例。</font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span><b><span class="15" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;&nbsp;</span></b>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<b><span class="15" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">&nbsp;2.<font face="宋体">胆道肿瘤及肝内外胆管结石：</font></span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">开放手术与微创技术相结合，重视围手术期处理，积累了丰富的经验，临床疗效良好。</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><b><span class="15" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">3.<font face="宋体">急性胰腺炎</font></span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">：对于各种原因的急性胰腺炎，包括妊娠合并急性胰腺炎的患者，坚持规范性与个体化治疗相结合，达到满意的效果。</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><b><span class="15" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">4.<font face="宋体">危重病救治</font></span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">：我科治疗的病人中，危重病救治占总治疗人数的<font face="Calibri">16%</font><font face="宋体">，承担了全院普外专业大部分危重病人的抢救治疗。</font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><b><span class="15" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">5.<font face="宋体">科研工作</font></span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">：承担国际科技合作重点项目，省科技计划项目等，科研经费近<font face="Calibri">1</font><font face="宋体">百万元，分别在</font><font face="Calibri">Tansplant&nbsp;&nbsp;proceedings</font><font face="宋体">及中华医学会系列期刊发表论文</font><font face="Calibri">10</font><font face="宋体">余篇，获军队科技进步三等奖</font><font face="Calibri">2</font><font face="宋体">项。</font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;</span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><p class="p"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</span><b><span class="15" style="font-family: &quot;Times New Roman&quot;;">6.<font face="宋体">教学工作</font></span></b><span style="font-size: 12pt;">：我科自<font face="Calibri">2006</font><font face="宋体">年开始招收培养硕士研究生，同时承担了本科生的教学工作。</font></span><span style="font-size: 12pt;"><o:p></o:p></span></p><!--EndFragment-->', NULL, 1, 1, '2017-04-02 21:57:15', '2017-04-02 21:57:15');
